n><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>% folding red, 查看嵌套测试 %<span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>% folding blue, 查看嵌套测试2 %<span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>% folding 查看嵌套测试3 %<span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>hahaha <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>span<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span>img <span class="token assign-left variable">src</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">'https://image.dbbqb.com/202101221115/7cdd741907c2ea150d054d24c4da6594/4d0G'</span> <span class="token operator">></span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span>/span<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>% endfolding %<span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>% endfolding %<span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>% endfolding %<span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
